  • What is the price of UMA today?

    Today, 8 September 2025, the price of UMA (UMA) is $1.37.

  • How do I add UMA to MetaMask?

    MetaMask automatically displays popular tokens like UMA（UMA）within your wallet. If you are not seeing your UMA in MetaMask, you can manually add it using the "Add to MetaMask" button above, over the price chart. Please remember that you first need to install MetaMask extension if you are on a PC or Mac (desktop computer). If you are on mobile, please check out our MetaMask Support guide here for more info.

  • How do I buy UMA?

    Buying UMA (UMA) in MetaMask wallet is speedy, simple, and safe. You can buy UMA (UMA) tokens directly in MetaMask using payment methods like a credit card, debit card, bank account, Apple Pay, Google Pay, or PayPal. There's no need for centralised exchanges. Select from thousands of your favourite tokens to buy on over 15 networks including Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, Linea, Base, and more.

  • How do I sell UMA?

    MetaMask makes it easy to sell your UMA (UMA) and convert your crypto to cash. You can exchange from MetaMask wallet directly to your debit card, credit card, PayPal, or bank account. By removing unnecessary steps and cutting excess fees, offramping your digital assets is fast and simple.

  • How do I swap UMA?

    Swapping UMA is simple and cost-effective with MetaMask. Choose from thousands of your favourite tokens across ten networks including Ethereum, Solana, Linea, Base, and Arbitrum. MetaMask Swaps also include gas fees right in your quotes, making swapping crypto as smooth as can be.

  • How do I bridge UMA?

    Bridging crypto across chains allows you to move tokens from one network to another. With MetaMask, bridging UMA (UMA) is easy, secure, and cost-effective. Our aggregator finds the most efficient routes to move your digital assets from one chain to another. And with cross-chain swapping, bridging and swapping can take place at the same time in a single transaction. Meaning: instead of bridging UMA from chain A and wrapping or unwrapping it on chain B, you can swap UMA from chain A to a second token on chain B, all in one move.

  • What is the price history of UMA?

    Today, 8 September 2025, the price of UMA (UMA) is $1.37. The all-time high of UMA (UMA) is $41.56. The all-time low of UMA (UMA) is $0.30. UMA (UMA)'s market capitalisation is $123,440,892.00.

  • What is UMA's all-time high?

    The all-time high of UMA (UMA) is $41.56.

  • What is UMA's all-time low?

    The all-time low of UMA (UMA) is $0.30.

  • What can you do with UMA?

    With UMA, you can send and receive UMA, the network's native token, and use it to pay transaction fees on certain networks. UMA is supported in decentralised apps for trading, staking, yield optimisation, and payments. You can participate in DeFi protocols, bridge assets between networks, or use UMA in select web3 financial strategies, all with Ethereum-compatible speed and flexibility.

  • How do I trade UMA for other cryptocurrencies?

    Trading UMA (UMA) for ETH, WBTC, or SOL can be done directly in MetaMask. For more information on how to swap UMA, head to MetaMask Support.
